overview: Filthy... Agent Filthy. License to thrill. He may not be able to dismantle a bomb, but he can get a wonder bra off that poor, unsuspecting female in 59 seconds or less without fast cars, fancy gadgets, or pricy alcohol. Your fellow pervs at Filthy Films know damn well which is the more valuable talent. This third installment of Agent Filthy 0069 sets its sizzling sites on brand new targets - lusty, busty targets that lurk in the shadows waiting to straddle our hero and ride him 'til he's too sore to be slick... or is it too slick to be sore? Either way - femme fatales have never had their defenses penetrated so hard. Agent Filthy: No tux. No bucks. Just hot, horny fucks.
title: Agent Filthy 0069: Mission 3
